item.title: CVE-2019-17101|2024-08-05T01:33:16.812Z -- netatmo -- smart%20indoor%20camera
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in a Command ('Command Injection') vulnerability in firmware versions prior to x.xx of Netatmo Smart Indoor Camera allows an attacker to execute commands on the device. This issue affects: Netatmo Smart Indoor Camera version and prior versions.
